text: Le Haut-Soultzbach is a commune in the Haut-Rhin department of north-east France. It started on 1 January 2016 by combining two previous communes, Mortzwiller and Soppe-le-Haut.Arrêté 23 October 2015 == References == Category:2016 establishments in France Category:Communes in Haut-Rhin
title: Le Haut-Soultzbach
